{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id77eb31b3-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s460vv–3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"460vv–3"},"text":"§ 460vv–3.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Administration","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subject to valid existing rights, each wilderness area designated by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s460vv–1"},"text":"section 460vv–1 of this title","children":[],"tail":" shall be administered by the Secretary of Agriculture in accordance with the provisions of the Wilderness Act of 1964 ["},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s1131"},"text":"16 U.S.C. 1131","children":[],"tail":" et seq.] governing areas designated by that Act as wilderness areas, except that with respect to any area designated in "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s460vv–1"},"text":"section 460vv–1 of this title","children":[],"tail":", any reference in such provisions to the effective date of the Wilderness Act of 1964 shall be deemed to be a reference to the effective date of this subchapter."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id77eb31b4-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/499/s5"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–499, § 5","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1988-10-18"},"text":"Oct. 18, 1988","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/102/2492"},"text":"102 Stat. 2492","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id77eb31b5-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id77eb31b6-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id77eb31b7-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Wilderness Act of 1964, referred to in text, probably means the Wilderness Act, ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/88/577"},"text":"Pub. L. 88–577","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1964-09-03"},"text":"Sept. 3, 1964","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/78/890"},"text":"78 Stat. 890","children":[],"tail":", which is classified generally to chapter 23 (§ 1131 et seq.) of this title. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s1131"},"text":"section 1131 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The effective date of the Wilderness Act of 1964, referred to in text, means ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1964-09-03"},"text":"Sept. 3, 1964","children":[],"tail":", the date of enactment of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/88/577"},"text":"Pub. L. 88–577","children":[],"tail":", which enacted chapter 23 of this title."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The effective date of this subchapter, referred to in text, means ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1988-10-18"},"text":"Oct. 18, 1988","children":[],"tail":", the date of enactment of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/499"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–499","children":[],"tail":", which enacted this subchapter."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
